  <name>Scripted Journeys</name>
  <summary>Play a multi-map text adventure</summary>
  
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-3.0-only</project_license>
  
  <description>
    <p>Scripted Journeys is a text-based adventure game where players can explore various maps, solve puzzles, and embark on exciting quests. The game features rich storytelling and a variety of maps to choose from, offering a unique experience each time you play. Discover hidden secrets and unravel mysteries in this engaging adventure.</p>
  </description>
  
